      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 8 Business Day article on plan by Ford Motor Co to distribute cash and shares to stockholders</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the Company News column of Business Day on Tuesday about the Ford Motor Company's plan to distribute cash and shares to stockholders misstated the amount of money allotted and the number of shares that will be outstanding. The company is distributing $5.7 billion in cash, not $6 billion. The shares outstanding will be 1.893 billion, not 1.9 billion.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A report in the Company News column of Business Day on Tuesday about the Ford Motor Company's plan to distribute cash and shares to stockholders misstated the amount of money allotted and the number of shares that will be outstanding. The company is distributing $5.7 billion in cash, not $6 billion. The shares outstanding will be 1.893 billion, not 1.9 billion.</p>
